#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:3
msgid "Attendance logs"
msgstr "Log absensi"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:5
msgid ""
"When entering the **Attendances** application, the :guilabel:`Overview` "
"dashboard is presented by default, and displays all the user's attendance "
"logs (their check in and check out information) for the current day. If the "
"user has the required :ref:`access rights <attendances/access-rights>` or is "
"an :ref:`approver <attendances/approvers>` for specific employees, those "
"employees' attendance logs also appear on the :guilabel:`Overview` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuka aplikasi **Absensi**, dashboard :guilabel:`Ikhtisar` "
"ditampilkan secara default, dan menampilkan semua log absensi user "
"(informasi check in dan check out mereka) untuk hari ini. Jika user "
"memiliki :ref:`hak akses <attendances/access-rights>` yang diperlukan atau "
"merupakan :ref:`pemberi persetujuan <attendances/approvers>` untuk karyawan "
"tertentu, log absensi karyawan tersebut juga muncul di "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Ikhtisar`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:11
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Overview` dashboard displays the current day, segmented by "
"hour, with the current hour highlighted in yellow. The appearance of "
"the :guilabel:`Overview` dashboard is determined by the :ref:`working "
"schedule <employees/schedule>` set on the employee's records. Each "
"employee's working hours appear in white, while all other hours appear in "
"gray. This allows managers to visually determine if an employee is working "
"outside of their working hours."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard :guilabel:`Ikhtisar` menampilkan hari ini, dibagi per jam, dengan "
"jam saat ini disorot dengan warna kuning. Tampilan "
"dashboard :guilabel:`Ikhtisar` ditentukan oleh :ref:`jadwal kerja <employees/"
"schedule>` yang ditetapkan pada catatan karyawan. Jam kerja setiap karyawan "
"ditampilkan dalam warna putih, sedangkan semua jam lainnya ditampilkan dalam "
"warna abu-abu. Ini memungkinkan manajer untuk secara visual menentukan "
"apakah seorang karyawan bekerja di luar jam kerja mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:17
msgid ""
"Employees populate the rows, alphabetically by first name. Each attendance "
"log displays the total hours along with the specific check in and check out "
"times. The log colors indicate the following statuses:"
msgstr ""
"Karyawan mengisi baris, secara alfabetis berdasarkan nama depan. Setiap log "
"absensi menampilkan total jam beserta waktu check in dan check out yang "
"spesifik. Warna log menunjukkan status berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:21
msgid "Gray: Completed entries where the employee has checked in and out."
msgstr ""
"Abu-abu: Entri yang telah selesai di mana karyawan telah check in dan check "
"out."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:22
msgid ""
"Green: Active entries where the employee checked in but has not yet checked "
"out."
msgstr "Hijau: Entri aktif di mana karyawan check in tetapi belum check out."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:23
msgid ""
"Red: Entries with any errors (e.g. employees have double entries, or forget "
"to check out)."
msgstr ""
"Merah: Entri dengan kesalahan apa pun (misalnya karyawan memiliki entri "
"ganda, atau lupa check out)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:None
msgid ""
"The overview dashboard presenting the information for the week, with the "
"current day\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard ringkasan yang menyajikan informasi untuk minggu tersebut, dengan "
"hari ini disorot."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:29
msgid ""
"A color-coded bar indicates how many hours out of the total expected hours "
"the employee has logged for the day. Rollover the color bar to view the "
"details for the employee's current day. Solid colors indicate the logged "
"hours (with both a start and end time), while pale colors indicate the "
"employee is signed in, but has not signed out yet. Only *completed* "
"attendance logs (records with a check in and check out time) appear in the "
"summary of the logged time."
msgstr ""
"Batang berkode warna menunjukkan berapa jam dari total jam yang diharapkan "
"yang telah dicatat karyawan untuk hari itu. Arahkan kursor ke batang warna "
"untuk melihat detail hari ini karyawan tersebut. Warna solid menunjukkan jam "
"yang tercatat (dengan waktu mulai dan akhir), sedangkan warna pucat "
"menunjukkan karyawan sudah sign in, tetapi belum sign out. Hanya log absensi "
"yang *selesai* (catatan dengan waktu check in dan check out) yang muncul "
"dalam ringkasan waktu yang tercatat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:36
msgid ""
"Abigail Peterson is scheduled to work from 9:00 AM to 12:00 PM, then take a "
"one-hour lunch break from 12:00 PM to 1:00 PM, then work from 1:00 PM to "
"6:00 PM, for a total of eight hours."
msgstr ""
"Abigail Peterson dijadwalkan bekerja dari pukul 9:00 pagi hingga 12:00 "
"siang, kemudian mengambil istirahat makan siang satu jam dari pukul 12:00 "
"siang hingga 1:00 siang, lalu bekerja dari pukul 1:00 siang hingga 6:00 "
"sore, dengan total delapan jam."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:39
msgid ""
"Abigails checks in at 9:00 AM, and checks out at 12:00 PM. She logs in again "
"at 1:00 PM. The current time is 2:15 PM. The rollover information displays "
"`3h / 8h`, indicating Abigail has logged three completed working hours out "
"of a total of eight. There is a pale green line that extends past the "
"summary block, indicating she checked in at 1:00 PM, but has not yet checked "
"out. The length of the pale green line indicates the time worked."
msgstr ""
"Abigail check in pada pukul 9:00 pagi, dan check out pada pukul 12:00 siang. "
"Dia log in lagi pada pukul 1:00 siang. Waktu saat ini adalah pukul 2:15 "
"siang. Informasi rollover menampilkan `3j / 8j`, yang menunjukkan Abigail "
"telah mencatat tiga jam kerja yang selesai dari total delapan jam. Ada garis "
"hijau pucat yang meluas melewati blok ringkasan, yang menunjukkan dia check "
"in pada pukul 1:00 siang, tetapi belum check out. Panjang garis hijau pucat "
"menunjukkan waktu yang bekerja."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:0
msgid ""
"The rollover green bar indicating Abigail logged 3 hours, and is currently "
"logged in."
msgstr ""
"Batang hijau rollover yang menunjukkan Abigail mencatat 3 jam, dan saat ini "
"sedang log in."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:48
msgid ""
"The **Attendances** dashboard allows for changing the displayed time period, "
"either :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, :guilabel:`Quarter`, :guilabel:`Year`, "
"or a custom time period. To instantly return the dashboard to the present "
"date, click the :guilabel:`Today` button at any time."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard **Absensi** memungkinkan untuk mengubah periode waktu yang "
"ditampilkan, "
"baik :guilabel:`Hari`, :guilabel:`Minggu`, :guilabel:`Bulan`, :guilabel:`Kuartal`, :guilabel:`Tahun`, "
"atau periode waktu khusus. Untuk langsung mengembalikan dashboard ke tanggal "
"sekarang, klik tombol :guilabel:`Hari Ini` kapan saja."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:54
msgid ""
"Any attendance logs that have errors appear in red, indicating they need to "
"be resolved by a user with the proper :ref:`access rights <attendances/"
"access-rights>` or are :ref:`approvers <attendances/approvers>` for the "
"employees with the errors."
msgstr ""
"Log absensi apa pun yang memiliki kesalahan muncul dalam warna merah, yang "
"menunjukkan bahwa kesalahan tersebut perlu diselesaikan oleh user "
"dengan :ref:`hak akses <attendances/access-rights>` yang tepat atau "
"merupakan :ref:`pemberi persetujuan <attendances/approvers>` untuk karyawan "
"yang memiliki kesalahan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:61
msgid "Filters and groups"
msgstr "Filter dan kelompok"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:63
msgid ""
"Sometimes, attendance officers and managers need to view specific records, "
"such as all automatic checkouts, to determine which employees chronically "
"forget to check out, or by department, to determine which team is working "
"the most overtime."
msgstr ""
"Terkadang, petugas absensi dan manajer perlu melihat catatan spesifik, "
"seperti semua checkout otomatis, untuk menentukan karyawan mana yang secara "
"kronis lupa check out, atau berdasarkan departemen, untuk menentukan tim "
"mana yang bekerja lembur paling banyak."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:67
msgid ""
"For these cases, use the search bar to select a :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`Filters` or :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Group By`, or "
"combine both to present the desired information."
msgstr ""
"Untuk kasus ini, gunakan bilah pencarian untuk memilih :icon:`fa-"
"filter` :guilabel:`Filters` atau :icon:`oi-group` :guilabel:`Group By`, atau "
"gabungkan keduanya untuk menyajikan informasi yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/attendances/attendance_logs.rst:74
