msgstr "Karyawan"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Employees** centralizes :doc:`personnel files <employees/"
"new_employee>`, employment :doc:`contracts <payroll/contracts>`, "
"and :doc:`departmental hierarchies <employees/departments>` in one system. "
"In addition, each employee record tracks :doc:`certifications <employees/"
"certifications>` and :doc:`training <employees/learning>`, "
"earned :doc:`badges <employees/badges>`, and all assigned :doc:`equipment "
"<employees/equipment>`. Customizable :doc:`onboarding <employees/"
"onboarding>` and :doc:`offboarding <employees/offboarding>` programs ensure "
"all employees are trained and ready for work, and all required steps are "
"taken when they leave."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Karyawan** memusatkan :doc:`file personel <employees/"
"new_employee>`, :doc:`kontrak <payroll/contracts>` kerja, dan :doc:`hierarki "
"departemen <employees/departments>` dalam satu sistem. Selain itu, setiap "
"catatan karyawan melacak :doc:`sertifikasi <employees/certifications>` "
"dan :doc:`pelatihan <employees/learning>`, :doc:`lencana <employees/badges>` "
"yang diperoleh, dan semua :doc:`peralatan <employees/equipment>` yang "
"ditugaskan. Program :doc:`onboarding <employees/onboarding>` "
"dan :doc:`offboarding <employees/offboarding>` yang dapat disesuaikan "
"memastikan semua karyawan dilatih dan siap bekerja, dan semua langkah yang "
"diperlukan diambil ketika mereka keluar."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:16
msgid ""
"Properly configuring the settings in the **Employees** app ensures the "
"dashboard shows each employee's real-time attendance and work location—data "
"that drives payroll accuracy, capacity planning, and compliance reporting."
msgstr ""
"Mengonfigurasi pengaturan dengan benar di aplikasi **Karyawan** memastikan "
"dashboard menampilkan absensi dan lokasi kerja setiap karyawan secara real-"
"time—data yang mendorong akurasi payroll, perencanaan kapasitas, dan "
"pelaporan kepatuhan."

