"Once the selections are made, you can export the report in different formats:"
msgstr ""
"Setelah pilihan dibuat, Anda dapat mengekspor laporan dalam berbagai format:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2500
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Export to PDF` to generate a printable version of the "
"Social Security certificate."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Ekspor ke PDF` untuk menghasilkan versi cetak sertifikat "
"Jaminan Sosial."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:2502
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Export to XLSX` to generate an Excel file containing all "
"relevant data."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Ekspor ke XLSX` untuk menghasilkan file Excel yang berisi "
"semua data relevan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/belgium.rst:None
msgid "Social Security Certificate PDF Header."
msgstr "Header PDF Sertifikat Jaminan Sosial."

