#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:55
msgid ""
":guilabel:`GSTIN`: Enter a 15-digit tax identification number required for "
"GST-registered businesses in India."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`GSTIN`: Masukkan nomor identifikasi pajak 15 digit yang "
"diperlukan untuk bisnis terdaftar GST di India."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PAN`: Enter a 10-character alphanumeric ID issued by the Income "
"Tax Department for tax reporting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PAN`: Masukkan ID alfanumerik 10 karakter yang dikeluarkan oleh "
"Departemen Pajak Penghasilan untuk pelaporan pajak."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:59
msgid ":guilabel:`Company ID`: Enter the business's state ID number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID Perusahaan`: Masukkan nomor ID negara bagian dari bisnis."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: By default, INR is selected. If not, select INR from "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mata Uang`: Secara default, INR dipilih. Jika tidak, pilih INR "
"dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:61
msgid ""
":guilabel:`UPI Id`: Enter a virtual payment address used for receiving "
"digital payments through India's UPI system."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`ID UPI`: Masukkan alamat pembayaran virtual yang digunakan untuk "
"menerima pembayaran digital melalui sistem UPI India."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:66
msgid ""
"Next, configure the payroll settings for the Indian payroll localization. "
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and "
"enable the following options that apply to the company:"
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, konfigurasikan pengaturan payroll untuk lokalisasi payroll "
"India. Navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Payroll --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`, dan aktifkan opsi berikut yang berlaku untuk perusahaan:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:70
msgid ""
":ref:`Employee Provident Fund <payroll/epf>`: Enter your :abbr:`EPF "
"(Employee Provident Fund)` Employer ID (alphanumeric code issued by "
"the :abbr:`EPFO (Employees' Provident Fund Organisation)`) to enable "
"automatic :abbr:`PF (Provident Fund)` deductions and contributions. Enabling "
"this will activate the **Provident Fund (PF) contribution** section in "
"employee payroll setting and contract template."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dana Cadangan Karyawan <payroll/epf>`: Masukkan ID Pemberi "
"Kerja :abbr:`EPF (Employee Provident Fund)` Anda (kode alfanumerik yang "
"diterbitkan oleh :abbr:`EPFO (Employees' Provident Fund Organisation)`) "
"untuk mengaktifkan pemotongan dan kontribusi :abbr:`PF (Provident Fund)` "
"otomatis. Mengaktifkan ini akan mengaktifkan bagian **Kontribusi Dana "
"Cadangan (PF)** dalam pengaturan payroll karyawan dan template kontrak."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:74
msgid ""
":ref:`Professional Tax <payroll/pt>`: Enter your state-issued :abbr:`PT "
"(Professional Tax)` registration number (usually numeric/alphanumeric) to "
"allow salary-based professional tax deduction. Enabling this will activate "
"the **Professional Tax slab** field under the **Tax Deductions** section in "
"employee payroll setting and contract template."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Pajak Profesional <payroll/pt>`: Masukkan nomor registrasi :abbr:`PT "
"(Professional Tax)` yang diterbitkan negara bagian Anda (biasanya numerik/"
"alfanumerik) untuk memungkinkan pemotongan pajak profesional berbasis gaji. "
"Mengaktifkan ini akan mengaktifkan kolom **Slab Pajak Profesional** di bawah "
"bagian **Pemotongan Pajak** dalam pengaturan payroll karyawan dan template "
"kontrak."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:78
msgid ""
":ref:`Employee State Insurance <payroll/esic>`: Enter your :abbr:`ESIC "
"(Employee State Insurance)` Employer Code/IP Number (10-digit numeric ID "
"provided by ESIC) to process mandatory medical insurance contributions. "
"Enabling this will activate the **ESIC (Employee State Insurance)** section "
"in employee payroll setting and contract template."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Asuransi Negara Karyawan <payroll/esic>`: Masukkan Kode Pemberi Kerja/"
"Nomor IP :abbr:`ESIC (Employee State Insurance)` Anda (ID numerik 10 digit "
"yang diberikan oleh ESIC) untuk memproses kontribusi asuransi kesehatan "
"wajib. Mengaktifkan ini akan mengaktifkan bagian **ESIC (Employee State "
"Insurance)** dalam pengaturan payroll karyawan dan template kontrak."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:82
msgid ""
":ref:`Labour Welfare Fund <payroll/lwf>`: Enter your :abbr:`LWF (Labour "
"Welfare Fund)` Establishment/Identification Number (state-issued numeric/"
"alphanumeric ID) to deduct and remit statutory welfare fund contributions. "
"Enabling this will activate the **Labour Welfare Fund (LWF)** section in "
"employee payroll setting and contract template."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Dana Kesejahteraan Tenaga Kerja <payroll/lwf>`: Masukkan Nomor "
"Pendirian/Identifikasi :abbr:`LWF (Labour Welfare Fund)` Anda (ID numerik/"
"alfanumerik yang diterbitkan negara bagian) untuk memotong dan menyerahkan "
"kontribusi dana kesejahteraan wajib. Mengaktifkan ini akan mengaktifkan "
"bagian **Dana Kesejahteraan Tenaga Kerja (LWF)** dalam pengaturan payroll "
"karyawan dan template kontrak."

